43struct dns_nta {
44 unsigned int magic;
45 isc_refcount_t refcount;
46 dns_ntatable_t *ntatable;
47 bool forced;
48 isc_timer_t *timer;
49 dns_fetch_t *fetch;
50 dns_rdataset_t rdataset;
51 dns_rdataset_t sigrdataset;
52 dns_fixedname_t fn;
53 dns_name_t *name;
54 isc_stdtime_t expiry;
55};
56
57#define NTA_MAGIC ISC_MAGIC('N', 'T', 'A', 'n')
58#define VALID_NTA(nn) ISC_MAGIC_VALID(nn, NTA_MAGIC)
59
60/*
61 * Obtain a reference to the nta object. Released by
62 * nta_detach.
63 */
64static void
65nta_ref(dns_nta_t *nta) {
66 isc_refcount_increment(&nta->refcount);
67}
68
69static void
70nta_detach(isc_mem_t *mctx, dns_nta_t **ntap) {
71 REQUIRE(ntap != NULL && VALID_NTA(*ntap));
72 dns_nta_t *nta = *ntap;
73 *ntap = NULL;
74
75 if (isc_refcount_decrement(&nta->refcount) == 1) {
76 isc_refcount_destroy(&nta->refcount);
77 nta->magic = 0;
78 if (nta->timer != NULL) {
79 (void)isc_timer_reset(nta->timer,
80 isc_timertype_inactive,
81 NULL, NULL, true);
82 isc_timer_detach(&nta->timer);
83 }
84 if (dns_rdataset_isassociated(&nta->rdataset)) {
85 dns_rdataset_disassociate(&nta->rdataset);
86 }
87 if (dns_rdataset_isassociated(&nta->sigrdataset)) {
88 dns_rdataset_disassociate(&nta->sigrdataset);
89 }
90 if (nta->fetch != NULL) {
91 dns_resolver_cancelfetch(nta->fetch);
92 dns_resolver_destroyfetch(&nta->fetch);
93 }
94 isc_mem_put(mctx, nta, sizeof(dns_nta_t));
95 }
96}
97
98static void
99free_nta(void *data, void *arg) {
100 dns_nta_t *nta = (dns_nta_t *) data;
101 isc_mem_t *mctx = (isc_mem_t *) arg;
102
103 nta_detach(mctx, &nta);
104}
105
106isc_result_t
107dns_ntatable_create(dns_view_t *view,
108 isc_taskmgr_t *taskmgr, isc_timermgr_t *timermgr,
109 dns_ntatable_t **ntatablep)
110{
111 dns_ntatable_t *ntatable;
112 isc_result_t result;
113
114 REQUIRE(ntatablep != NULL && *ntatablep == NULL);
115
116 ntatable = isc_mem_get(view->mctx, sizeof(*ntatable));
117 if (ntatable == NULL)
118 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
119
120 ntatable->task = NULL;
121 result = isc_task_create(taskmgr, 0, &ntatable->task);
122 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
123 goto cleanup_ntatable;
124 isc_task_setname(ntatable->task, "ntatable", ntatable);
125
126 ntatable->table = NULL;
127 result = dns_rbt_create(view->mctx, free_nta, view->mctx,
128 &ntatable->table);
129 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
130 goto cleanup_task;
131
132 result = isc_rwlock_init(&ntatable->rwlock, 0, 0);
133 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
134 goto cleanup_rbt;
135
136 ntatable->timermgr = timermgr;
137 ntatable->taskmgr = taskmgr;
138
139 ntatable->view = view;
140 ntatable->references = 1;
141
142 ntatable->magic = NTATABLE_MAGIC;
143 *ntatablep = ntatable;
144
145 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
146
147 cleanup_rbt:
148 dns_rbt_destroy(&ntatable->table);
149
150 cleanup_task:
151 isc_task_detach(&ntatable->task);
152
153 cleanup_ntatable:
154 isc_mem_put(view->mctx, ntatable, sizeof(*ntatable));
155
156 return (result);
157}
158
159void
160dns_ntatable_attach(dns_ntatable_t *source, dns_ntatable_t **targetp) {
161 REQUIRE(VALID_NTATABLE(source));
162 REQUIRE(targetp != NULL && *targetp == NULL);
163
164 RWLOCK(&source->rwlock, isc_rwlocktype_write);
165
166 INSIST(source->references > 0);
167 source->references++;
168 INSIST(source->references != 0);
169
170 RWUNLOCK(&source->rwlock, isc_rwlocktype_write);
171
172 *targetp = source;
173}
174
175void
176dns_ntatable_detach(dns_ntatable_t **ntatablep) {
177 bool destroy = false;
178 dns_ntatable_t *ntatable;
179
180 REQUIRE(ntatablep != NULL && VALID_NTATABLE(*ntatablep));
181
182 ntatable = *ntatablep;
183 *ntatablep = NULL;
184
185 RWLOCK(&ntatable->rwlock, isc_rwlocktype_write);
186 INSIST(ntatable->references > 0);
187 ntatable->references--;
188 if (ntatable->references == 0)
189 destroy = true;
190 RWUNLOCK(&ntatable->rwlock, isc_rwlocktype_write);
191
192 if (destroy) {
193 dns_rbt_destroy(&ntatable->table);
194 isc_rwlock_destroy(&ntatable->rwlock);
195 if (ntatable->task != NULL)
196 isc_task_detach(&ntatable->task);
197 ntatable->timermgr = NULL;
198 ntatable->taskmgr = NULL;
199 ntatable->magic = 0;
200 isc_mem_put(ntatable->view->mctx, ntatable, sizeof(*ntatable));
201 }
202}
203
204static void
205fetch_done(isc_task_t *task, isc_event_t *event) {
206 dns_fetchevent_t *devent = (dns_fetchevent_t *)event;
207 dns_nta_t *nta = devent->ev_arg;
208 isc_result_t eresult = devent->result;
209 dns_ntatable_t *ntatable = nta->ntatable;
210 dns_view_t *view = ntatable->view;
211 isc_stdtime_t now;
212
213 UNUSED(task);
214
215 if (dns_rdataset_isassociated(&nta->rdataset))
216 dns_rdataset_disassociate(&nta->rdataset);
217 if (dns_rdataset_isassociated(&nta->sigrdataset))
218 dns_rdataset_disassociate(&nta->sigrdataset);
219 if (nta->fetch == devent->fetch)
220 nta->fetch = NULL;
221 dns_resolver_destroyfetch(&devent->fetch);
222
223 if (devent->node != NULL)
224 dns_db_detachnode(devent->db, &devent->node);
225 if (devent->db != NULL)
226 dns_db_detach(&devent->db);
227
228 isc_event_free(&event);
229 isc_stdtime_get(&now);
230
231 switch (eresult) {
232 case ISC_R_SUCCESS:
233 case DNS_R_NCACHENXDOMAIN:
234 case DNS_R_NXDOMAIN:
235 case DNS_R_NCACHENXRRSET:
236 case DNS_R_NXRRSET:
237 if (nta->expiry > now)
238 nta->expiry = now;
239 break;
240 default:
241 break;
242 }
243
244 /*
245 * If we're expiring before the next recheck, we might
246 * as well stop the timer now.
247 */
248 if (nta->timer != NULL && nta->expiry - now < view->nta_recheck)
249 (void) isc_timer_reset(nta->timer, isc_timertype_inactive,
250 NULL, NULL, true);
251 nta_detach(view->mctx, &nta);
252}
253
254static void
255checkbogus(isc_task_t *task, isc_event_t *event) {
256 dns_nta_t *nta = event->ev_arg;
257 dns_ntatable_t *ntatable = nta->ntatable;
258 dns_view_t *view = ntatable->view;
259 isc_result_t result;
260
261 if (nta->fetch != NULL) {
262 dns_resolver_cancelfetch(nta->fetch);
263 nta->fetch = NULL;
264 }
265 if (dns_rdataset_isassociated(&nta->rdataset))
266 dns_rdataset_disassociate(&nta->rdataset);
267 if (dns_rdataset_isassociated(&nta->sigrdataset))
268 dns_rdataset_disassociate(&nta->sigrdataset);
269
270 isc_event_free(&event);
271
272 nta_ref(nta);
273 result = dns_resolver_createfetch(view->resolver, nta->name,
274 dns_rdatatype_nsec,
275 NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0,
276 DNS_FETCHOPT_NONTA, 0, NULL,
277 task, fetch_done, nta,
278 &nta->rdataset,
279 &nta->sigrdataset,
280 &nta->fetch);
281 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
282 nta_detach(view->mctx, &nta);
283}
284
285static isc_result_t
286settimer(dns_ntatable_t *ntatable, dns_nta_t *nta, uint32_t lifetime) {
287 isc_result_t result;
288 isc_interval_t interval;
289 dns_view_t *view;
290
291 REQUIRE(VALID_NTATABLE(ntatable));
292 REQUIRE(VALID_NTA(nta));
293
294 if (ntatable->timermgr == NULL)
295 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
296
297 view = ntatable->view;
298 if (view->nta_recheck == 0 || lifetime <= view->nta_recheck)
299 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
300
301 isc_interval_set(&interval, view->nta_recheck, 0);
302 result = isc_timer_create(ntatable->timermgr, isc_timertype_ticker,
303 NULL, &interval, ntatable->task,
304 checkbogus, nta, &nta->timer);
305 return (result);
306}
307
308static isc_result_t
309nta_create(dns_ntatable_t *ntatable, const dns_name_t *name,
310 dns_nta_t **target)
311{
312 dns_nta_t *nta = NULL;
313 dns_view_t *view;
314
315 REQUIRE(VALID_NTATABLE(ntatable));
316 REQUIRE(target != NULL && *target == NULL);
317
318 view = ntatable->view;
319
320 nta = isc_mem_get(view->mctx, sizeof(dns_nta_t));
321 if (nta == NULL)
322 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
323
324 nta->ntatable = ntatable;
325 nta->expiry = 0;
326 nta->timer = NULL;
327 nta->fetch = NULL;
328 dns_rdataset_init(&nta->rdataset);
329 dns_rdataset_init(&nta->sigrdataset);
330
331 isc_refcount_init(&nta->refcount, 1);
332
333 nta->name = dns_fixedname_initname(&nta->fn);
334 dns_name_copy(name, nta->name, NULL);
335
336 nta->magic = NTA_MAGIC;
337
338 *target = nta;
339 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
340}
341
342isc_result_t
343dns_ntatable_add(dns_ntatable_t *ntatable, const dns_name_t *name,
344 bool force, isc_stdtime_t now,
345 uint32_t lifetime)
346{
347 isc_result_t result;
348 dns_nta_t *nta = NULL;
349 dns_rbtnode_t *node;
350 dns_view_t *view;
351
352 REQUIRE(VALID_NTATABLE(ntatable));
353
354 view = ntatable->view;
355
356 result = nta_create(ntatable, name, &nta);
357 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
358 return (result);
359
360 nta->expiry = now + lifetime;
361 nta->forced = force;
362
363 RWLOCK(&ntatable->rwlock, isc_rwlocktype_write);
364
365 node = NULL;
366 result = dns_rbt_addnode(ntatable->table, name, &node);
367 if (result == ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
368 if (!force)
369 (void)settimer(ntatable, nta, lifetime);
370 node->data = nta;
371 nta = NULL;
372 } else if (result == ISC_R_EXISTS) {
373 dns_nta_t *n = node->data;
374 if (n == NULL) {
375 if (!force)
376 (void)settimer(ntatable, nta, lifetime);
377 node->data = nta;
378 nta = NULL;
379 } else {
380 n->expiry = nta->expiry;
381 nta_detach(view->mctx, &nta);
382 }
383 result = ISC_R_SUCCESS;
384 }
385
386 RWUNLOCK(&ntatable->rwlock, isc_rwlocktype_write);
387
388 if (nta != NULL)
389 nta_detach(view->mctx, &nta);
390
391 return (result);
392}
393
394/*
395 * Caller must hold a write lock on rwlock.
396 */
397static isc_result_t
398deletenode(dns_ntatable_t *ntatable, const dns_name_t *name) {
399 isc_result_t result;
400 dns_rbtnode_t *node = NULL;
401
402 REQUIRE(VALID_NTATABLE(ntatable));
403 REQUIRE(name != NULL);
404
405 result = dns_rbt_findnode(ntatable->table, name, NULL, &node, NULL,
406 DNS_RBTFIND_NOOPTIONS, NULL, NULL);
407 if (result == ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
408 if (node->data != NULL)
409 result = dns_rbt_deletenode(ntatable->table,
410 node, false);
411 else
412 result = ISC_R_NOTFOUND;
413 } else if (result == DNS_R_PARTIALMATCH)
414 result = ISC_R_NOTFOUND;
415
416 return (result);
417}
418
419isc_result_t
420dns_ntatable_delete(dns_ntatable_t *ntatable, const dns_name_t *name) {
421 isc_result_t result;
422
423 RWLOCK(&ntatable->rwlock, isc_rwlocktype_write);
424 result = deletenode(ntatable, name);
425 RWUNLOCK(&ntatable->rwlock, isc_rwlocktype_write);
426
427 return (result);
428}

430bool
431dns_ntatable_covered(dns_ntatable_t *ntatable, isc_stdtime_t now,
432 const dns_name_t *name, const dns_name_t *anchor)
433{
434 isc_result_t result;
435 dns_fixedname_t fn;
436 dns_rbtnode_t *node;
437 dns_name_t *foundname;
438 dns_nta_t *nta = NULL;
439 bool answer = false;
440 isc_rwlocktype_t locktype = isc_rwlocktype_read;
441
442 REQUIRE(ntatable == NULL || VALID_NTATABLE(ntatable));
443 REQUIRE(dns_name_isabsolute(name));
444
445 if (ntatable == NULL)
446 return (false);
447
448 foundname = dns_fixedname_initname(&fn);
449
450 relock:
451 RWLOCK(&ntatable->rwlock, locktype);
452 again:
453 node = NULL;
454 result = dns_rbt_findnode(ntatable->table, name, foundname, &node, NULL,
455 DNS_RBTFIND_NOOPTIONS, NULL, NULL);
456 if (result == DNS_R_PARTIALMATCH) {
457 if (dns_name_issubdomain(foundname, anchor))
458 result = ISC_R_SUCCESS;
459 }
460 if (result == ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
461 nta = (dns_nta_t *) node->data;
462 answer = (nta->expiry > now);
463 }
464
465 /* Deal with expired NTA */
466 if (result == ISC_R_SUCCESS && !answer) {
467 char nb[DNS_NAME_FORMATSIZE];
468
469 if (locktype == isc_rwlocktype_read) {
470 RWUNLOCK(&ntatable->rwlock, locktype);
471 locktype = isc_rwlocktype_write;
472 goto relock;
473 }
474
475 dns_name_format(foundname, nb, sizeof(nb));
476 isc_log_write(dns_lctx, DNS_LOGCATEGORY_DNSSEC,
477 DNS_LOGMODULE_NTA, ISC_LOG_INFO,
478 "deleting expired NTA at %s", nb);
479
480 if (nta->timer != NULL) {
481 (void) isc_timer_reset(nta->timer,
482 isc_timertype_inactive,
483 NULL, NULL, true);
484 isc_timer_detach(&nta->timer);
485 }
486
487 result = deletenode(ntatable, foundname);
488 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
489 isc_log_write(dns_lctx, DNS_LOGCATEGORY_DNSSEC,
490 DNS_LOGMODULE_NTA, ISC_LOG_INFO,
491 "deleting NTA failed: %s",
492 isc_result_totext(result));
493 }
494 goto again;
495 }
496 RWUNLOCK(&ntatable->rwlock, locktype);
497
498 return (answer);
499}

501static isc_result_t
502putstr(isc_buffer_t **b, const char *str) {
503 isc_result_t result;
504
505 result = isc_buffer_reserve(b, strlen(str));
506 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
507 return (result);
508
509 isc_buffer_putstr(*b, str);
510 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
511}
512
513isc_result_t
514dns_ntatable_totext(dns_ntatable_t *ntatable, const char *view,
515 isc_buffer_t **buf)
516{
517 isc_result_t result;
518 dns_rbtnode_t *node;
519 dns_rbtnodechain_t chain;
520 bool first = true;
521 isc_stdtime_t now;
522
523 REQUIRE(VALID_NTATABLE(ntatable));
524
525 isc_stdtime_get(&now);
526
527 RWLOCK(&ntatable->rwlock, isc_rwlocktype_read);
528 dns_rbtnodechain_init(&chain, ntatable->view->mctx);
529 result = dns_rbtnodechain_first(&chain, ntatable->table, NULL, NULL);
530 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS && result != DNS_R_NEWORIGIN) {
531 if (result == ISC_R_NOTFOUND)
532 result = ISC_R_SUCCESS;
533 goto cleanup;
534 }
535 for (;;) {
536 dns_rbtnodechain_current(&chain, NULL, NULL, &node);
537 if (node->data != NULL) {
538 dns_nta_t *n = (dns_nta_t *) node->data;
539 char nbuf[DNS_NAME_FORMATSIZE];
540 char tbuf[ISC_FORMATHTTPTIMESTAMP_SIZE];
541 char obuf[DNS_NAME_FORMATSIZE +
542 ISC_FORMATHTTPTIMESTAMP_SIZE +
543 sizeof("expired: \n")];
544 dns_fixedname_t fn;
545 dns_name_t *name;
546 isc_time_t t;
547
548 /*
549 * Skip "validate-except" entries.
550 */
551 if (n->expiry != 0xffffffffU) {
552 name = dns_fixedname_initname(&fn);
553 dns_rbt_fullnamefromnode(node, name);
554 dns_name_format(name, nbuf, sizeof(nbuf));
555 isc_time_set(&t, n->expiry, 0);
556 isc_time_formattimestamp(&t, tbuf,
557 sizeof(tbuf));
558
559 snprintf(obuf, sizeof(obuf), "%s%s%s%s: %s %s",
560 first ? "" : "\n", nbuf,
561 view != NULL ? "/" : "",
562 view != NULL ? view : "",
563 n->expiry <= now
564 ? "expired"
565 : "expiry",
566 tbuf);
567 first = false;
568 result = putstr(buf, obuf);
569 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
570 goto cleanup;
571 }
572 }
573 result = dns_rbtnodechain_next(&chain, NULL, NULL);
574 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS && result != DNS_R_NEWORIGIN) {
575 if (result == ISC_R_NOMORE)
576 result = ISC_R_SUCCESS;
577 break;
578 }
579 }
580
581 cleanup:
582 dns_rbtnodechain_invalidate(&chain);
583 RWUNLOCK(&ntatable->rwlock, isc_rwlocktype_read);
584 return (result);
585}
586
587isc_result_t
588dns_ntatable_dump(dns_ntatable_t *ntatable, FILE *fp) {
589 isc_result_t result;
590 isc_buffer_t *text = NULL;
591 int len = 4096;
592
593 result = isc_buffer_allocate(ntatable->view->mctx, &text, len);
594 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
595 return (result);
596
597 result = dns_ntatable_totext(ntatable, NULL, &text);
598
599 if (isc_buffer_usedlength(text) != 0) {
600 (void) putstr(&text, "\n");
601 } else if (result == ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
602 (void) putstr(&text, "none");
603 } else {
604 (void) putstr(&text, "could not dump NTA table: ");
605 (void) putstr(&text, isc_result_totext(result));
606 }
607
608 fprintf(fp, "%.*s", (int) isc_buffer_usedlength(text),
609 (char *) isc_buffer_base(text));
610 isc_buffer_free(&text);
611 return (result);
612}
613
614isc_result_t
615dns_ntatable_save(dns_ntatable_t *ntatable, FILE *fp) {
616 isc_result_t result;
617 dns_rbtnode_t *node;
618 dns_rbtnodechain_t chain;
619 isc_stdtime_t now;
620 bool written = false;
621
622 REQUIRE(VALID_NTATABLE(ntatable));
623
624 isc_stdtime_get(&now);
625
626 RWLOCK(&ntatable->rwlock, isc_rwlocktype_read);
627 dns_rbtnodechain_init(&chain, ntatable->view->mctx);
628 result = dns_rbtnodechain_first(&chain, ntatable->table, NULL, NULL);
629 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS && result != DNS_R_NEWORIGIN)
630 goto cleanup;
631
632 for (;;) {
633 dns_rbtnodechain_current(&chain, NULL, NULL, &node);
634 if (node->data != NULL) {
635 isc_buffer_t b;
636 char nbuf[DNS_NAME_FORMATSIZE + 1], tbuf[80];
637 dns_fixedname_t fn;
638 dns_name_t *name;
639 dns_nta_t *n = (dns_nta_t *) node->data;
640
641 /*
642 * Skip this node if the expiry is already in the
643 * past, or if this is a "validate-except" entry.
644 */
645 if (n->expiry <= now || n->expiry == 0xffffffffU) {
646 goto skip;
647 }
648
649 name = dns_fixedname_initname(&fn);
650 dns_rbt_fullnamefromnode(node, name);
651
652 isc_buffer_init(&b, nbuf, sizeof(nbuf));
653 result = dns_name_totext(name, false, &b);
654 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
655 goto skip;
656
657 /* Zero terminate. */
658 isc_buffer_putuint8(&b, 0);
659
660 isc_buffer_init(&b, tbuf, sizeof(tbuf));
661 dns_time32_totext(n->expiry, &b);
662
663 /* Zero terminate. */
664 isc_buffer_putuint8(&b, 0);
665
666 fprintf(fp, "%s %s %s\n", nbuf,
667 n->forced ? "forced" : "regular",
668 tbuf);
669 written = true;
670 }
671 skip:
672 result = dns_rbtnodechain_next(&chain, NULL, NULL);
673 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS && result != DNS_R_NEWORIGIN) {
674 if (result == ISC_R_NOMORE)
675 result = ISC_R_SUCCESS;
676 break;
677 }
678 }
679
680 cleanup:
681 dns_rbtnodechain_invalidate(&chain);
682 RWUNLOCK(&ntatable->rwlock, isc_rwlocktype_read);
683
684 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
685 return (result);
686 else
687 return (written ? ISC_R_SUCCESS : ISC_R_NOTFOUND);
688}
